profile:
Perfect Turf is the leading synthetic turf brand in Western Canada and one of the oldest, most established artificial turf companies in Canada. Our Calgary and Vancouver teams have a combined 40 years experience and have helped train artificial turf installers across Canada. You will not find more experienced installation teams in Alberta or British Columbia.

Our sales and installation teams have installed thousands of synthetic grass projects, while prioritizing superior installations and excellent customer service. 
  

Prioritizing Our Clients
Perfect Turf offers you an environmentally-friendly turf solution that will make you the envy of the neighbourhood. We pride ourselves on good old-fashioned hard work and customer service, using only the best quality, North American-made turf.

  
Delivering Superior Quality
We will not sell or install an inferior product to mislead you into thinking you are getting a good short-term deal. We know that working with only the highest quality products and performing installations to the absolute highest standards is what sets us apart from the competition. Because of our commitment to quality in every aspect we are proud to offer a complete 10-Year warranty on both the turf and installation. Ultimately, our success is attributed to maintaining a balance of high quality products, competitive prices and excellent customer service. 
  
Providing Industry-Leading Experience
We have performed almost every type of installation possible, including anything from small dog runs up to full size artificial athletic fields. No job is too big or too small for our teams.

Our favourite projects include replacing your hard to maintain front or back yard with a beautiful maintenance-free synthetic lawn. Because we're dog lovers, some of our most satisfying projects are replacing destroyed pet yards with our synthetic grass K9 system.

profile:
Clayâ€™s Lawn and Snow Inc. specializes in sod installation, commercial snow removal, and commercial lawn maintenance. We are based out of Airdrie, but our commercial lawn services and sod installation cover the whole city of Calgary and surrounding areas. Our commercial snow removal and parking lot sanding/salting  stays only in the north part of Calgary and Airdrie . However we welcome all commercial  inquiries for large commercial properties outside this area.

We are a well established business, based for 7 years in Ontario, and the past 6 years in Airdrie/Calgary. Our experienced crew takes pride in their dependability and quality workmanship. We are committed to offering our customers premium service at an affordable cost.

We have some of the best equipment in the industry allowing us to take on any job. The right equipment means getting the job done quickly, getting the job done right, and being able to do so at a very competitive price.
